docs.doc:
Return Object Models (PowerShell Pipeline Compatible):
- DateRangeResult: { DateTime Date, DateCriteriaType Criteria }
- LogFileInfo: { FileInfo File, DateTime LogDate, DateCriteriaType DateSource }
- LogFolderInfo: { DirectoryInfo Folder, DateTime ParsedDate, string FolderNamePattern }
- ArchiveInfo: { FileInfo ArchiveFile, string CompressionEngine, long CompressedSize, long OriginalSize, TimeSpan CompressionDuration }
All models must be C# record types with init-only properties.
